<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8203088>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Female of Ictinogomphus distinctus from Futala Lake, Nagpur, Maharashtra, India, on 06.10.2013. (a) dorsum of head; (b) lateral view of head; (c) dorsum of thorax; (d) dorsum of S1–S2; (e) lateral view of S8–10; (f) dorsal view of S10 including caudal appendages; (g) vulvar scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203088/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8203090>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ictinogomphus spp. from India. (a–b) female of I. distinctus from Nagpur, Maharashtra on 18.10.2008; (c) male of I. distinctus from Madhya Pradesh on 06.09.2016; (d) female of I. rapax from Odisha on 24.05.2014. (Photos: a to b—A.D. Tiple; c—V. Sharma; d—A. Payra)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203090/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

